[[FIFA Club World Cup]]|name=|group=}}||0||22||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!128||18||8||1||15||0||24||3||3||0||178||22\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!366||66||21||6||27||5||24||3||9||2||447||82\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n===International===\n{{updated|match played 27 March 2018}}<ref name=NFT>{{NFT player |id=54072 |name=Lallana, Adam |accessdate=30 December 2018}}</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=6|[[England national football team|England]]\n|2013||2||0\n|-\n|2014||11||0\n|-\n|2015||6||0\n|-\n|2016||10||3\n|-\n|2017||4||0\n|-\n|2018||1||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total||34||3\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''As of match played 27 March 2018. England score listed first, score column indicates score after each Lallana goal.''<ref name=NFT/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|+ International goals by date, venue, cap, opponent, score, result and competition\n|-\n!scope=col|No.\n!scope=col|Date\n!scope=col|Venue\n!scope=col|Cap\n!scope=col|Opponent\n!scope=col|Score\n!scope=col|Result\n!scope=col|Competition\n!scope=col class=unsortable|{{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|1\n|4 September 2016||[[\u0160tadi\u00f3n Antona Malatinsk\u00e9ho]], Trnava, Slovakia||align=center|27||{{fb|Slovakia}}||align=center|1\u20130||align=center|1\u20130||[[2018 FIFA World Cup qualification]]||align=center|<ref name=\"goal 040916\"/>\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|2\n|11 November 2016||[[Wembley Stadium]], London, England||align=center|28||{{fb|Scotland}}||align=center|2\u20130||align=center|3\u20130|||[[2018 FIFA World Cup qualification]]||align=center|<ref name=\"goal 111116\"/>\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|3\n|15 November 2016||[[Wembley Stadium]], London, England||align=center|29||{{fb|Spain}}||align=center|1\u20130||align=center|2\u20132||[[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]||align=center|<ref>{